criteria.textblock:
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  > 18 years of age;

          -  laboratory or clinical-epidemiological confirmation of COVID-19 (history of close or
             home contact with a laboratory-confirmed case who has fever or at least one of the
             respiratory signs or symptoms, in the last 14 days after contact, and for which it was
             not possible to carry out the specific laboratory investigation)

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Immunosuppressed patients of any kind;

          -  Pregnant women;

          -  More than 14 days from the onset of symptoms;

          -  Not accept participation or non-signature of the IC;

          -  Undiagnosed cases, suspected or probable.
